{"_path":"/maps/_ai/benchmark/simple","_dir":"benchmark","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"Simple Benchmark","description":"日常使用的简单基准测试","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"_2025-12"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2025-12"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"使用老朋友测 Kimi K2 Thinking、GPT-5 和 DeepSeek V3.2："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.kimi.com/share/19af7152-2b22-8e9f-8000-000016cfd092","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Kimi K2 Thinking"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：没有展示抽象能力，但通过少量枚举，意外地找到了几组不错的答案。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://chat.deepseek.com/share/bpg5qaiwq5fuk7addd","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"DeepSeek V3.2"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：通过数万token的枚举，找到了几组不错的答案，此外衍生出了关于“含义对立”的思路。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.maxai.co/share?id=a5222cc57cbc97e4830bf86724d1b1b8851ebc3d0614f2112961e160","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"GPT-5"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：第一轮就找到了不错的答案，此外思路绝佳。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"无论我的系统提示词是什么，本地 Qwen3 Next 直接拒绝了我的任务，除非我把 GPT-5 的思路拔下来告诉他要怎么找答案。本地的 Qwen3 Next Thinking 则是花了四分钟烧掉 1w token，找到两个错误答案和一个“诺/no”。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"Local Qwen3 Next","src":"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/20251208131758762.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"_2025-03"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2025-03"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"SVD 的全称"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在一个关于“教材”的变量名隐喻中，如果 SVD 中 D 的解释是 Director，那么全称可能是什么？正确答案是什么？4o、QwQ 和 Kimi 把答案导向了数学，但经过追问，话题相关低代码、组件、编译原理之类的，和数学没有关系。那么 SVD 是什么？4o 说是 Structure View Director，即数据结构视图导演。我觉得这个回答接近正确答案，而其他两个乱答。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"翻译问题","src":"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202503182351515.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"GPT-4o（MaxAI）关于“billion”的翻译犯了很明显的错误。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://chat.qwen.ai/s/2efd38e7-c682-493b-a479-8c1f31e0a2f5","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"找到一个中文单词，和某个英文单词读音相近，但是意思完全相反 @QwQ-32B"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"","src":"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202503070241843.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"非联网。在很开头就找到了\"buy\"和\"卖\"，但是居然没有从这里推理出正确结果（尽管最终答案包含\"buy\"和\"卖\"）。继续问相同的问题，经过 2 分半的思考，找到了“爱”和“hate”，不算是可接受的答案。下次直接试试：“找十组中文单词，这些中文单词和某个英文单词的发音相近，但两者的意思完全相反”。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://metaso.cn/s/IpfAIch","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如何解读：Business is Business @metaso"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"搜索资料选的是“学术”，但是表现出乎意料的差，根本没有把握句子的意思。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"_2024-11"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2024-11"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":